channel.title: [Decompiled]+[Original] RuneScape's Log-in Applet [Original]+[Decompiled]
channel.description:
I was messing around with the Java Cache Viewer again, and took a look at RuneScape's Log-In applet. I'm not sure if this is in right section, or what it can be used for, I just wanted to release to the community. If there is any way of using this, please let me know. If not, tell me and I'll remove.
Original link for loader: http://www.runescape.com/loginapplet/loginapplet--6bf2be5f-2031170585.jar Decompiled version: http://rapidshare.com/files/288327925/loginapplet--6bf2be5f-2031170585.rar.html
